title: Winning numbers drawn in 'Keno' game
maintext:
OLYMPIA, Wash. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Friday evening’s drawing of the Washington Lottery’s “Keno” game were:
11-15-17-20-22-25-34-36-41-42-44-46-48-50-53-59-61-72-73-75
(eleven, fifteen, seventeen, twenty, twenty-two, twenty-five, thirty-four, thirty-six, forty-one, forty-two, forty-four, forty-six, forty-eight, fifty, fifty-three, fifty-nine, sixty-one, seventy-two, seventy-three, seventy-five)
